description._content: Original Collection: Harriet's Collection Item Number: HC0596 Image Description: The Corvallis Creamery was located on First Street, south of Madison. The creamery was established in 1897, and this facility was built between 1900 and 1910. You can find this image by searching for the item number by clicking here. Want more? You can find more digital resources online.
